text: Iserlohn (Westphalian Low German: Iserlaun, Iserliaun, or Iserlauhn; Middle Low German: Eisenwald) is a city in North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany. About 93,000 people live there; it is one of the largest cities in that region. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:MÃ¤rkischer Kreis
